n class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 48px; list-style-position: outside;"><li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps19"> <span class="rvts56">The button</span> <img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement63.png"> <span class="rvts56">to add a counter.</span> </li></ul><p class="rvps19"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"><img width="353" height="163" alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement62.png"></p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56">Confirm with the key</span> <img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement61.png"> <span class="rvts56">The counter appears in the menu.</span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement60.png"></p><h2 class="rvps17"><a name="_Toc474480705"></a> <span class="rvts0"><span class="rvts57">Remove a counter.</span></span> </h2><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 48px; list-style-position: outside;"><li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps19"> <span class="rvts56">The button</span> <img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement59.png"> <span class="rvts56">to remove a counter.</span> </li></ul><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56">Select the counter to remove from the drop down menu and use the button</span> <img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement58.png"> <span class="rvts56">.</span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement57.png"></p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56">Confirm the message to delete the counter.</span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement56.png"></p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><h2 class="rvps17"><a name="_Toc474480706"></a> <span class="rvts0"><span class="rvts57">Rename a counter.</span></span> </h2><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 48px; list-style-position: outside;"><li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps19"> <span class="rvts56">The button</span> <img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement55.png"> <span class="rvts56">to rename a counter.</span> </li></ul><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56">Select the counter to rename and click the button</span> <img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement54.png"> <span class="rvts56">.</span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps2"><img width="700" height="72" alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement53.png"></p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56">Change the name and confirm with the OK button.</span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"><img width="316" height="145" alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement52.png"></p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><h2 class="rvps17"><a name="_Toc474480707"></a> <span class="rvts0"><span class="rvts57">General Options.</span></span> </h2><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56">The button</span> <img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement51.png"> <span class="rvts56">allows you to set the general options.</span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps2"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement50.png"></p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"><span class="rvts56"> </span></p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56">The counters can be stored in either an XML file or an SQL database</span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts63">XML file:</span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 48px; list-style-position: outside;"><li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps19"> <span class="rvts56">Location of the XML file counters:</span> </li></ul><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps16"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement49.png"></p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56">This parameter defines the location of the XML file counters.</span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56">If the XML file is moved (eg a server), you can set the new location with the button</span> <img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement48.png"> <span class="rvts56">.</span> </p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 48px; list-style-position: outside;"><li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps19"> <span class="rvts56">options:</span> </li></ul><p class="rvps16"><img width="692" height="98" alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement47.png"></p><p class="rvps16"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56">This option creates a .csv file (one per meter) containing the history of the values used in the counters.</span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56">By default this file is saved in the folder &#39;&#39; SmartCounter logs &#39;&#39; which is in the installation folder</span> <span class="rvts58"><span class="rvts56">SmartProperties.</span></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63">SQL database:</span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts58">SmartCounter</span> <span class="rvts56">can also be used with a SQL database</span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps2"><img width="486" height="366" alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement46.png"></p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts63"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56">The location and the SQL login credentials are then filled beings</span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56">The following buttons allow you to import or export your database SmartCounter:</span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps2"><img alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement45.png"></p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 48px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps22"> <span class="rvts56">Import an XML in the SQL database, simply select the XML file to be imported:</span> </li></ul><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps2"><img width="527" height="303" alt="" style="padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/NouvelElement44.png"></p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts56"><br></span> </p><p class="rvps20"> <span class="rvts